ime":"2020-12-07T12:19:51.000Z","msg":"me<br />\nhea 人做hea 工"},{"pid":"ecfad440133cfd31f4e01bcc1b4bbf713fa91d20","tid":2314580,"uid":190023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0479f8f33e330bff2ac1b857f754dc59825e5f6d","tid":2314580,"uid":100633,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:57:51.000Z","msg":"fg啱啱返第一份全職，以前一直好迷惘，唔鍾意自己讀嗰科嘅工作。上個月搵到一份自己好有興趣，甚至係強項嘅工作，原來真係好正，做自己愛做的事，真係好有滿足感，廿幾年嚟第一次咁肯定自己嘅價值！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家加油！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"係咩工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a08aec5fe7024b21b2af070c2f335752bc2a3f","tid":2314580,"uid":189711,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"4b2becd63da1b455398efc28821842baa3aaaf00","tid":2314580,"uid":192465,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"quote":{"pid":"fb9f0ce5e19db673092f43f579ab826a3c9d2acb","tid":2314580,"uid":98899,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"連自己想做咩都唔知  唔太惡頂都做㗎啦  咁所人真係想知自己做咩咩"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T23:54:39.000Z","msg":"因為個社會令你連認識自己既機會都冇<br />\n中小學填鴨教育<br />\n大學又唔可以揀乞食科<br />\n一早已經已經潛而默化左你唔可以追求興趣<br />\n畢業又要鬥快搵工<br />\n做緊野既又唔敢裸辭<br />\n儲舊小錢買樓結婚就更加唔使再諗自己想點<br />\n好多人都係咁庸碌一生"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"講得好中係自己都完全唔認識自己(我估HK大部份人都係咁?)<br />\n諗返起讀書簡科畢業搵工都一定聽老師前輩講過話要follow your heart 追尋自己夢想，但問題核心係根本連自己都唔知自己想做咩，有咩achievement goal想達成 ，好似做左20幾年人白做咁<br />\n<br />\n個狀態時間耐左，其實同機器無分別，成世人都係為左成就他人，讀書就做白老鼠咩DSE比個制度玩，做野就唔知做乜鳩咁應付日常開支交稅，成為社會中無自由意志可有可無的一粒齒輪，比最頂果層人勞役，用份糧買起左自己人生咁。<br />\n<br />\n所以好提子一 D好知道自己想點的人，好有目標，究竟點樣做到，而自己做唔到佢地個境界"},{"pid":"99231e229bd551a55b7d92e48c4770846044d6b1","tid":2314580,"uid":100633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecfad440133cfd31f4e01bcc1b4bbf713fa91d20","tid":2314580,"uid":190023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0479f8f33e330bff2ac1b857f754dc59825e5f6d","tid":2314580,"uid":100633,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:57:51.000Z","msg":"fg啱啱返第一份全職，以前一直好迷惘，唔鍾意自己讀嗰科嘅工作。上個月搵到一份自己好有興趣，甚至係強項嘅工作，原來真係好正，做自己愛做的事，真係好有滿足感，廿幾年嚟第一次咁肯定自己嘅價值！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家加油！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"係咩工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc673eefa19bb0e0632d9b66c974b577b6c74020","tid":2314580,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:44:35.000Z","msg":"我，返工日日都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪好奇怪"},{"pid":"ed0a2db757f4a6b2f0a36ad47a20b67ab2e510c7","tid":2314580,"uid":226355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc673eefa19bb0e0632d9b66c974b577b6c74020","tid":2314580,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:44:35.000Z","msg":"我，返工日日都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪好奇怪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:47:23.000Z","msg":"都唔係，我都試過<br />\n不過做耐左覺得係時候跳出comfort zone <br />\n點知真係好難搵得返自己enjoy既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f411da149895c45c0165cb75311b434c56265f","tid":2314580,"uid":56425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed0a2db757f4a6b2f0a36ad47a20b67ab2e510c7","tid":2314580,"uid":226355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc673eefa19bb0e0632d9b66c974b577b6c74020","tid":2314580,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:44:35.000Z","msg":"我，返工日日都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪好奇怪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:47:23.000Z","msg":"都唔係，我都試過<br />\n不過做耐左覺得係時候跳出comfort zone <br />\n點知真係好難搵得返自己enjoy既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上一份工做得幾開心，做既野自己擅長，老細同事欣賞我，又有work life balance。只係做耐咗就覺得開始唔多野學，少少悶，人工又想再高啲，想趁後生再搏盡啲<br />\n<br />\n結果轉咗工就發現上一份工係天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34252fd59dffa4d5e124de58a19e4e908453e5ba","tid":2314580,"uid":250995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b2b55675b3fa6647434f971d8e511c291eb83ef","tid":2314580,"uid":226355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28436c9b0e4260ace7f805aaffa48e86e529a1a9","tid":2314580,"uid":250995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8902e1ae958f131e076bd682f35e70bee636a837","tid":2314580,"uid":56425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"如果做緊，想知係做咩<br />\n<br />\n我覺得社會上超過九成人都係為份糧<br />\n叫做啱做就繼續做<br />\n好少真係好鐘意份工既工作內容<br />\n<br />\n其實諗落好唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾多人放棄夢想，成世人勞勞碌碌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:56:32.000Z","msg":"香港真係好多人跟住主流走，冇思考過乜嘢生活方式啱自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"識得咁諗既人都已經好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"我就係覺得香港已經太多唔快樂嘅打工仔 唔需要多我一個 <br />\n於是大學轉major 為咗做自己鐘意嘅職業<br />\n搵得唔多 但對得住自己 將勞力付出喺自己鐘意嘅嘢度"},{"pid":"d51e758d8b4ab58478fc41c6c8238d95f7dc235f","tid":2314580,"uid":126397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"師兄我都明白你嘅感受，我之前返嗰份工一開始都覺得好開心，但係做耐左就覺得營營役役，又要shift，番到屋企又夜，又冇乜發展空間，最後做咗年幾就quit咗，把心一橫去讀書，讀自己鍾意嘅嘢。<br />\n我都睇得出師兄你曾經都有做過自己開心滿足嘅工作，亦都好努力想突破自己，我認同樓上講要做一個快樂嘅打工仔，如果現實可以嘅話，邊個想唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你會唔會再想揾返work life balance？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2318ff6c861b51d2a7e18a4308ff2c744462a350","tid":2314580,"uid":301589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"每份工頭幾個月都以為係做緊想做嘅嘢  結果都係無份做得長"},{"pid":"b8d8a19aca907de575f336db9afe3da32d39fde7","tid":2314580,"uid":209418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:54:57.000Z","msg":"我想過啲簡單嘅日子，唔需要畀社會/親友限制我想做嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係冇嘗試過<br />\n<br />\n我試過做地盤整親搞到搬唔到重嘢，啲痛一直斷唔到尾。<br />\n<br />\n做sales又唔夠人口才好，成日畀人捽數，不斷改變自己都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n我冇已經話要喺香港買樓上車，只係想冇經濟壓力,過啲開心簡單嘅日子,點解咁難<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界公平咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想要自由。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n但香港根本冇自由呢一樣嘢"},{"pid":"153299dc95e5dd5f6dc846347d02108c124d6648","tid":2314580,"uid":218551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"庸庸碌碌半生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ead27faffdffcb8f84afc9af813b02c1bee7439","tid":2314580,"uid":191107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"屋企仲吹快D拍拖結婚，但就黎連自己都養唔掂,點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435fbe33a6bdf07def41ba9af60106bb1e74da06","tid":2314580,"uid":22030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049022965b3b91cf650fb3fde3c904bfb33da28a","tid":2314580,"uid":56425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d51e758d8b4ab58478fc41c6c8238d95f7dc235f","tid":2314580,"uid":126397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"師兄我都明白你嘅感受，我之前返嗰份工一開始都覺得好開心，但係做耐左就覺得營營役役，又要shift，番到屋企又夜，又冇乜發展空間，最後做咗年幾就quit咗，把心一橫去讀書，讀自己鍾意嘅嘢。<br />\n我都睇得出師兄你曾經都有做過自己開心滿足嘅工作，亦都好努力想突破自己，我認同樓上講要做一個快樂嘅打工仔，如果現實可以嘅話，邊個想唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你會唔會再想揾返work life balance？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"最後去咗讀咩？宜家過成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過多幾年我都會想搵返work life balance<br />\n我宜家份工係好chur，但勝在人工高，做多兩年就應該儲到幾球做首期+結婚，所以頂住先<br />\n<br />\n只係有時受完氣，OT完返去自己捱飯盒，就忍唔住諗 : 其實除咗人工，我仲有啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟我可以捱多幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 捱完我可以去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037fd3fa35cf20938989353b3612d6f93d6e8a67","tid":2314580,"uid":80367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d2e61c253777c55f1fd67ab7390d55110cccff","tid":2314580,"uid":211878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:31:54.000Z","msg":"我會對部份task有心機研究下 覺得幾有趣咁<br />\n但又唔肯定自己係咪洗咗自己腦先會覺得啲嘢有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難判斷 <br />\n但會享受多嘢做做到夠鐘走人 多過無嘢做要望住個鐘等放"},{"pid":"81b9a7774af1bdf7f604d5a3068ceb60c61d1735","tid":2314580,"uid":76727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:37:52.000Z","msg":"返緊一份自己想做既工作<br />\n但一場武漢肺炎令到我呢行進入冰河時期<br />\n屌你老母中國。"},{"pid":"52f8096fef1b990792ea56a6a355c4a1fe756ae4","tid":2314580,"uid":147031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3af5391fb8a44cab2f821b43d4947a8d3898f1fb","tid":2314580,"uid":375135,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"8902e1ae958f131e076bd682f35e70bee636a837","tid":2314580,"uid":56425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"如果做緊，想知係做咩<br />\n<br />\n我覺得社會上超過九成人都係為份糧<br />\n叫做啱做就繼續做<br />\n好少真係好鐘意份工既工作內容<br />\n<br />\n其實諗落好唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b