<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878a4eea83af51bfd9bed8f29db5b2caed14499a","tid":2314580,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26a41d40238d37f7dfce7d2c1054afd0eb4dfb7b","tid":2314580,"uid":190940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b2becd63da1b455398efc28821842baa3aaaf00","tid":2314580,"uid":192465,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"quote":{"pid":"fb9f0ce5e19db673092f43f579ab826a3c9d2acb","tid":2314580,"uid":98899,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"連自己想做咩都唔知  唔太惡頂都做㗎啦  咁所人真係想知自己做咩咩"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T23:54:39.000Z","msg":"因為個社會令你連認識自己既機會都冇<br />\n中小學填鴨教育<br />\n大學又唔可以揀乞食科<br />\n一早已經已經潛而默化左你唔可以追求興趣<br />\n畢業又要鬥快搵工<br />\n做緊野既又唔敢裸辭<br />\n儲舊小錢買樓結婚就更加唔使再諗自己想點<br />\n好多人都係咁庸碌一生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:25:01.000Z","msg":"講得好啱<br />\n唔係點會咁多人走去做政府office工日日重重複複<br />\n就係為咗一份穩定嘅人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"講到你出邊都唔係蟲蟲福福咁"},{"pid":"9360d3d759300d1ec158744f69177c19048ac8dc","tid":2314580,"uid":75712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f411da149895c45c0165cb75311b434c56265f","tid":2314580,"uid":56425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed0a2db757f4a6b2f0a36ad47a20b67ab2e510c7","tid":2314580,"uid":226355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc673eefa19bb0e0632d9b66c974b577b6c74020","tid":2314580,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:44:35.000Z","msg":"我，返工日日都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪好奇怪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:47:23.000Z","msg":"都唔係，我都試過<br />\n不過做耐左覺得係時候跳出comfort zone <br />\n點知真係好難搵得返自己enjoy既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"我都係<img s